OL,5,G0155 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FIt's a busy night at Barnsley
OL,7,     FHopsital's casualty department, so
OL,8,     Fwhen Sister Benita arrives to head
OL,9,     Fthe shift, the corridors are
OL,10,     Falready packed full of patients.
OL,11,G0245 Skin A&E
OL,12,     FDr Natalia Spierings tackles one
OL,13,     Fof the biggest lipomas of her
OL,14,     Fcareer, Dr Emma McMullen helps a
OL,15,     Fbride six weeks before 'I do'; and
OL,16,     FDr Adil Sheraz treats a patient
OL,17,     Fwith a face cyst.
OL,18,G0335 Home and Away
